<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Product Data Updated Notification</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #444">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto">
      <header
        style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px; text-align: center"
      >
        <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #1abc9c; font-size: 28px">
          Product Data Updated Notification
        </h1>
      </header>
      <main style="padding: 20px">
        <p>Dear {{username}},</p>
        <p>
          This is to inform you that your product "{{productName}}" has been
          updated due to "{{updateReason}}".
        </p>
        <p>
          We would like to remind you that it is your responsibility to ensure
          that the information you provide is accurate and up-to-date. Please
          review the updated information and make any necessary changes to
          ensure that it complies with our terms and conditions.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to
          contact our friendly customer support team at support@swiftmarket.com.
          We are always here to help and happy to answer any questions you may
          have.
        </p>
        <p>Thank you for your understanding and cooperation in this matter.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>{{adminUsername}} - SwiftMarket</p>
      </main>
      <footer
        style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px; text-align: center"
      >
        <p style="margin: 0">&copy; 2023 SwiftMarket. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
